Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys um let's see what's your energy um resist resist she can't resist here's a person\Nwe've used throughout as a test subject throughout here you use you just listen to heavy metal music
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,resist think of somebody you love resist i just want you to witness that uh listening to that\Nheavy metal music only for a few minutes blew out our acupuncture system do what i do think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of somebody you love smile and go ha ha ha ha ha ha ha okay now we fixed it okay which arm up\Nresist okay you're fixed i'm fixed but you notice that the music blew you out and uh it'll blow you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,out for about 20 minutes uh combat two those things where you tear the guts out of other\Nhuman beings and uh destroying other animals and shoot and kill and murder um have extremely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,negative energies\Num
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have a whole adolescent generation blowing out their acupuncture system\Num programming themselves into negativity with uh endless computer games in which they program
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves to kill kill kill kill kill kill and of course the more and better you kill the higher\Nthe score you get so what you're training yourself is to become an automated killer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in which your reflex is you see the difficulty with um computer games and this kind of music\Nand all and then you throw in drugs and you're like oh my god i'm gonna die i'm gonna die
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in this\Nthe most round yeah you're in a state of so when you listen to rap music saying kill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the cops\Nuh you play computer games that program you millions of times millions of times to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,maim rip asunder etc and you listen to music like this so you put on earphones now it has\Nnothing to do with what you think about it i like the rolling stones um the energy of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the rolling stones is positive\NNo. The energy of the beetles is positive. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. The beetles put out, let it be.\NThe stones put out, let it bleed. That gives you a little hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have a whole generation concerned with killing guns on TV.\NThey watch homicides, and they play killer games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They listen to rock music, and then you throw in drugs.\NSo with the drugs, you're in a very suggestible hypnotic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens to these people is they become dominated by negative energy fields.\NTheir consciousness becomes dominated by the attractor energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can demonstrate this over and over again.\NSo the rise of street crime and criminal activity by adolescents,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the public is well advised to be alarmed.\NThese people are programmed negative killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just waiting.\NAnd there was one on TV the other night who shot another one of his young classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked why he did it, he said he didn't know.\NNo, he didn't know. He's in an unconscious hypnotic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He just pulled the trigger.\NThe same as he does on combat, you know, the same as the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the negative lyrics of this kind of music are pounded into your consciousness\Nin a highly suggestible hypnotic state in which your negative...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,your energy fields are already negative.\NAnd that's why it's so complicated by the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real tragedy of modern society,\Nis that a whole generation of youth is being wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole generation is being wiped out by computer games, heavy metal rock, every cover.\NAnd we've tested every kind of music, and of course classical music makes you go strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,country western makes you go strong, reggae, soft rock makes you go strong.\NWe did a study, which I mentioned in the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at Sedona Villa, cocaine addicts after discharge,\Nthose who continued to listen to heavy metal rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the recovery rate was zero.\NZero percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, nobody recovered if they continued to hang out in that energy field.\NIs it the music itself? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the music itself.\NIt's the energy that accompanies that music.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology is a great research tool for parapsychology.\NThe current techniques used in parapsychology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to either prove or disprove a phenomena are equally fallacious.\NYou can't prove or disprove the presence of other invisible entities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by using infrared or Geiger counters or ultraviolet.\NI mean, those are all in a different domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove the immaterial in the universe\Nby using techniques that are suitable for the material universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use...\NLady, come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guy who makes a living running around\Nknocking parapsychology, the great Randy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the great Randy is positive. Resist.\NThe energy of the great Randy is negative. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He emanates a very negative energy\Nbecause his motivation is to disprove the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the gross dedication to...\NAlso, it's based on a false premise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you can imitate a phenomena,\Ntherefore you've negated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's obviously fallacious.\NYou can imitate any real phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but by imitating it doesn't disprove\Nthat the real phenomena actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought that parapsychology,\Nbecause a lot of people are interested in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,its use in politics and government,\Nof course, is extremely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's test out the government's present policy\Non...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the president's war on drugs is positive. Resist.\NIt's effective. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's political BS. Resist.\NIt's political BS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The war on drugs, the energy of it is over 160. Resist.\NIt's about 150. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The war on drugs calibrates at 150.\NIt's already a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's see what we would need\Nto effectively affect the war on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The government's program would have to calibrate\Nover 350. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 360. 350.\NYou'd have to have a program,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,government program funded program,\Nthat calibrates at 350 to handle the drug problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot handle a drug problem\Nwith a program that calibrates only at 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's used in politics, it's used in sociology,\Nit's used in politics, are endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought sort of an interesting one\Nhas to do with psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the so-called false memory syndrome.\NMore and more lawsuits are being brought against therapists
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,who inculcate false memories.\NLet's just check out this whole false memory syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These memories of our early childhood sexual abuse\Nthat are foggy and really only come to life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,via the therapist,\Nthose are real memories, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are false over 60% of the time,\N70% of the time, 80% of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the time.\NI get that these repressed memories
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of childhood sexual abuse\Nare false about 80% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One out of five, it actually happened,\Nfour out of five, it's false.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinesiology demonstrates this very well.\NLots of innocent people have been accused,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,lives have been destroyed,\Nfamilies have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody forgets that Freud discovered that\Nat the beginning of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All his female patients laying down on the couch,\Nsomewhere along the analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they would remember early childhood incestuous fantasies.\NAt first, Freud was flabbergasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought, how can all these fathers\Nbe molesting all these little girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just statistically, from a criminologic viewpoint,\Nthe percentage of the population
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that does this kind of thing\Nis very, very small, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it be?\NThen he found that these were
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious fantasies, incestuous,\Nand of course, this was part of the Oedipal complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Society has gone into repression\Nand unconsciousness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the return of the repressed,\Nand now tries to make it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it real?\NBecause you can be compensated for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Victimhood really pays in today's world.\NTherefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the use of kinesiology can be very, very useful\Nin psychological research in general,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as theory goes,\Nand as far as an individual case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think now of an individual case\Nof a patient I'm treating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The sexual abuse which took place in her childhood\Nwas real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NYes, it was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't BS.\NThe case I'm thinking about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the childhood sexual abuse was real.\NThis is one that was suggested to a patient of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by a therapist, you know.\NThe idea here, the way the scenario goes is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything before I was eight years old.\NInstantly, the therapist figures,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, there must have been a lot of sexual abuse.\NThese are people who have not been trained
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in psychoanalytic theory, you know.\NChildhood amnesia is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal people don't remember what happened\Nup until they were five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the rest of the story.\NIt has to do with the resolution of the edible complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, in my view of it,\Ncurrent pop psychology does not explain phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of current pop psychology\Nhaving to do with this repressed memory
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and all this kind of stuff,\Nand it's supposed to contribute to eating disorders,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bulimia, and all these kind of things,\Nis scientifically accurate, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's funny.\NFreudian theory is much closer to the truth about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Freudian theory is a lot closer to the truth about it.\NSo that's the false memory syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The mode in which I've been using it\Nand describing it in the book
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the field of consciousness\Nand especially that field called spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just test out some of the,\Nbecause this affects the lives of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a fellow right here.\NYou want to hold that over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This man's energy is positive.\NIt's over 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 550.\N540.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,About 540 is the energy.\NYou see, in the book he wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson, the founder of AA,\Nthe language of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 500s is the language of the heart.\NSo people who were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you calibrate what was their level of consciousness\Nwhen they came into this life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,people who calibrated in the 500s\Nare preoccupied with love and its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is love, how to define love,\Nthe difference between spiritual love and personal love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how to let go of attachments,\Nand love, you might say, universally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The meaning of love.\NNow let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got 540.\NHere's, I mentioned before, A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles is very interesting.\NWe'll see why in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 590, resist.\NIt calibrates over 610, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 599, resist.\N600.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,620.\N600.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates approximately at 600.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that again.\NA Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be more specific.\NThe workbook in A Course in Miracles calibrates at 600, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook calibrates over 600, resist.\NThe textbook is a little less useful than the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's interesting about this\Nis that 600 is the level at which form
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to disappear into formless.\NAnd 600 is also exactly the level of kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason people have used kinesiology for many years\Nwill still say, I don't believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it is that level at which\Nthe ego is not familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego dominates the levels below 600.\NThe ego does not dominate from 600 on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a different aspect of the ego,\Nthe spiritual ego dominates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ego is not used to working\Nat 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600 or over.\NSo anything 600 or over,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so the scientific people who\Npoo-poo anything that is not within
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical, mechanical, measurable domain,\Ndo so because their level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as we've seen, goes up to 499.\NThey can't comprehend things in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't get essence.\NThey don't get significance beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the measurable domain.\NIn fact, there was a recent article in Science
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that said something about\Nthere is no reality except
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that which can be measured.\NI think the name of the article was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is Measurement.\NSo, reality is measurement
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is a level at 499.\NBecause that which we all consider
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,worth dying for,\Nand people in the 500s and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with the non-measurable.\NThese are people willing to die for love,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for sacrifice,\Nfor the welfare of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For spiritual principles.\NThose are not measurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't weigh them.\NThey don't even exist anywhere in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're universal.\NSo let's move up the people then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one bit even higher.\NHere we have the Bhagavad Gita,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,revered of ancient Hindu wisdom,\Nand it calibrates over 700,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,750,\N740,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,740.\NHere's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,these are very interesting people.\NThey are enlightened gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in our time.\NTypically with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the teachings of Jesus, etc.\NOr Buddha is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,after 2000 years,\Npeople who didn't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what it meant in the first place,\Nrepeated it to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who didn't understand\Nwhat it meant in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And nobody really has any idea\Nwhat Jesus Christ said, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,\Nyou know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you put together everything\Nin the Bible and the New Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that Jesus Christ said,\Nit doesn't cover more than a few pages, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, in those years,\Nhe gave all kinds of lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These are interesting people.\NThis is Nisargadatta Maharaj,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who only died in the 80s.\NAnd he's an enlightened guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of his book is,\Nwell, what he spoke about was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he identified with awareness itself\Nbeyond consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very high level consciousness.\NNisargadatta Maharaj is 700, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 750, resist.\N710,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,720,\N730,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the low 700s.\NHere's another guru of recent vintage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a saint,\NSri Ramana Maharshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He died about 1958.\NSo let's just ask with this whole bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of this spiritual teacher\Nis over 700,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,720,\N730,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,740,\N750,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the low 700s.\NSo, that which the world calls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,really pure spiritual teachers,\Nreal gurus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not false ones.\NLet's check out another supposed guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because one use of this\Nis to tell the false from the true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NWhat's the name of the organ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.\NRajneesh has a positive energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Nwhat's the other one in India
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that stresses out our beauty?\NSai Baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai Baba.\NThe energy is positive, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NSo, a lot of the ones that people in the new age,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, go ooh and ahh over.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty there is that the error,\Nthe spiritual error,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is on such a level,\Nit's beyond the awareness of the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the naive spiritual student,\Nhis consciousness goes up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The guru goes up to here.\NTherefore, he seems impressive to the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the guru himself\Nis out because his integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is out on a level of consciousness\Nthat is beyond the student's capacity to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can see where that guru is out\Nis somebody who himself has been
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to that level and beyond.\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who tells you they're higher than Jesus Christ\Nis a false guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no being on the planet\Nthat has ever been higher than Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been a being on this planet\Nwhose consciousness was higher than that of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NYou know who claims that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims it all the time to various people.\NLucifer claims to be higher than Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NIt's Lucifer that thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you see demonstration of power,\Nmoney, collections of automobiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and riches, you see,\NRamana Maharshi lived a life of absolute simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even bother with a plate.\NHe ate off a leaf in native style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To say that you're as high or higher than Jesus Christ\Nis obviously fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha calibrates over 990,\Nover 1,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,over 1,100.\NKrishna calibrates about 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The great avatar is calibrated at 1,000.\NThe human body is capable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of coexisting with a consciousness\Ngreater than 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that,\Nas one says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when one's consciousness approaches 1,000,\Nthat seems to me the capacity of the human nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I say that is that subjectively,\Non January 10, 1965,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness that came on here was 850.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The nervous system was able to handle that energy.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:21:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NThe energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the miraculous event,\Nsuddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that which had been disappeared,\Nand instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an infinite presence,\Ninfinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean infinite presence,\Nof power so awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that the individual mind of the person\Nthat had been called dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,\Nstopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It never had another thought.\NIt had no will of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one with the presence,\Nand it's the presence that speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the presence that\Nacts through the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,here,\Nwhich the world calls David,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but that is just a...\NIn theology and spiritual truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is called awareness\Nis also in English called Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NThat which is consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,pure consciousness,\Nis called God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is,\Nbecause it's beyond existence and nonexistence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond truth and nontruth,\Nbecause it is that out of which
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself arose,\Nis the absolute Godhead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond which there is nothing.\NAnd out of the Godhead arose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite potentiality.\NSo as you go into a divine space,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the divinity of all things.\NWell, that's divinity expressing itself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,from formlessness into form.\NSo God is therefore the creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness,\Nwhich is not different than God,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is the creator of all things visible and invisible.\NAwareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's beyond all things visible and invisible,\Nis the Godhead out of which Godness arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked a lot about spirituality\Nand theology and causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kitty wanted to be part of it.\NYou can hear her meow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:23:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in some other parts of the video.\NLet's check out Kitty's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty's consciousness is positive.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty...\Nis very responsive to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NShe's attuned to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NWell, the reason I wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,get Kitty in the picture is because\Nconsciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we talk about consciousness,\Neverybody thinks we're talking about human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is vast,\Nand it goes way beyond human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes within the physical domain\Nup to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond a thousand,\Nwe go into other domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness is...\NWhen I say I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that's consciousness itself.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NSo, now let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to talk about causality from a different level.\NWe talked about causality from a Newtonian viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality within the Newtonian viewpoint,\Nwhich goes up to about 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we talked about causality here in this tape.\NWe talked about cause being on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.26,0:24:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in the invisible realm,\Nand that the world we see is a world of effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.87,0:24:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is obvious when you're in the 500s.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.96,0:24:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is still true when you're beyond 600.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NAs you go beyond 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.72,0:24:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what you see is that time does not flow.\NTime, in reality, with a capital R,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,time stands still.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a holographic universe.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.41,0:24:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is actually happening as you go beyond 600,\Nyou see that this is a holographic universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.68,0:25:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in the universe sends off a vibration.\NThe acupuncture system, the etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is like an antenna that both sends and receives.\NYou see that there is an intersection of the vibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.84,0:25:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of the essence of all things radiating forth\Nin a standing hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.06,0:25:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what seems to,\Nthe illusion that something is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.37,0:25:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see,\Nin reality, nothing is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.37,0:25:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.69,0:25:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, there are no events.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NSo, what seems like motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when you walk through a hologram,\Nas I walk around a hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.08,0:25:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems to move.\NYou know, everybody's had the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at least in an art gallery,\Nyou walk along and the eyes seem to follow you as you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.08,0:26:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, having a fixed level of motion,\Na level of perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.04,0:26:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a function of the ego\Nto fix one's perception to a given point,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as you move around the hologram,\Nit seems to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.64,0:26:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what seems to be events\Nare really not events at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.09,0:26:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?\NAs you move around the hologram,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.85,0:26:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you get the illusion.\NSo, below the level of 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.92,0:26:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the level below 600 is the world of duality, resist.\NThe world beyond 600
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.11,0:26:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is the world of non-duality, resist.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.36,0:26:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as you move into a higher state of awareness,\Nwhat you see is that all things are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.07,0:26:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, there is no here or there, resist.\NAll things coexist simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.45,0:26:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere present, resist.\NYou see, the vibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.63,0:27:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the vibrations which exist,\Nwhich are registered by consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.17,0:27:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is not like a radio wave.\NIt doesn't, like, start here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and go there.\NThe thought that I hold right this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.39,0:27:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is as it's held everywhere present\Nthroughout the universe and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like on everywhere instantly.\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.46,0:27:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said in theology,\Nall hearts are open and all thoughts are known
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.10,0:27:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the mind of God, resist, resist.\NThat's a true signal, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.03,0:27:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness,\Nthe entire field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.09,0:27:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is equivalent to the mind of God, resist.\NIt's what people refer to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.70,0:27:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when they talk about the mind of God, resist.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.76,0:28:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind of God goes beyond consciousness\Nonto the level of awareness, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.72,0:28:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Godhead beyond consciousness.\NThe awareness is the Godhead, resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.02,0:28:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which consciousness arises, resist.\NSo,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.92,0:28:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're all antennas\Nand we all vibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.92,0:28:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at a frequency\Nthat's instantly available
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.92,0:28:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere in the universe,\Nthis would be a good way
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.92,0:28:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate with astronauts, resist.\NYeah, it would be a great way
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.30,0:28:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate with astronauts.\NYou can see logically on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.30,0:28:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you could know everything they're thinking,\Nfeeling, saying what they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.39,0:28:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a grand way to communicate.\NAnd I just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.87,0:28:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that's another practical thing\Nthat's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When we said consciousness\Nis far more than just human consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.70,0:29:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking about realms\Nthat the world calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.12,0:29:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,religion calls,\Nangelic, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.56,0:29:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 1,000 are the levels\Nof the angelic realms, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.10,0:29:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that was interesting.\NSo, we saw that a lot of gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.10,0:29:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,get up to 740.\NThere seems to be stopping off points.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.32,0:29:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are critical spiritual gates\Nwhich one goes through, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.32,0:29:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like,\Nit seems like large masses
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.76,0:29:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or smaller masses you go,\Nreach certain levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.24,0:29:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it's like a bunch of people\Nthat stand outside a certain gate
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.76,0:29:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's some kind of\Na critical spiritual awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.14,0:29:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that has to take place\Nto get beyond the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.55,0:29:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The great block that I was concerned about\Nand one of the reasons I wrote the book
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.71,0:30:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was in our world, reason,\Nreason seems to be the great blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people get beyond reason.\NWhen you push reason to its ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.00,0:30:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up at the level of genius, resist.\N499 is the level that the world
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.99,0:30:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,considers genius, resist.\NVery few people get beyond 499, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.31,0:30:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we said 0.4% of the world's population\Ngets beyond 499, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.72,0:30:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so it's the great blockade, reason.\NThe opening of the heart then
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.65,0:30:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,opens up love\Nand then 600 is the next big gate
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.00,0:30:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,going from duality into non-duality.\NThen I haven't really checked out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.22,0:30:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels from 700 on up,\Nbut we noticed before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:31:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when we were doing the tapes\Nthat Maharaj, Nisargadatta Maharaj,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.68,0:31:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi,\Nthere seems to be a number of gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.00,0:31:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the low 700s.\NHuang Po, Huang Po calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.13,0:31:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,over 700, resist.\N740, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.71,0:31:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,750, resist.\N740, there seems to be another great gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\N740 is the level of the mystic, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.79,0:31:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystic has mastered\Nthe spiritual domain and our world, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He has mastered also the physical world, resist.\NOkay, to go through the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.24,0:31:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from 740 up to 800,\None has to maybe master both the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the physical, resist, simultaneously,\Nresist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.52,0:32:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there seems to be a great gap\Nfrom 740 on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a gap.\NI can only go back on my own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.96,0:32:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a confrontation\Nat 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.24,0:32:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At 800 is another gate, resist.\NAt 800, one has to personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.57,0:32:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in quotes,\Nface Lucifer himself, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.76,0:32:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To reach 850 means\None has what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.63,0:32:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Included within the domain of one's\Nawareness, consciousness, and mastery
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.10,0:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of Lucifer, resist.\NYeah, it's like one pulls up one's opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:33:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, what's the energy\Nof Lester Levinson, resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.74,0:33:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of Babaji, resist.\NThat's a being that fell
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.29,0:33:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the confrontation with Lucifer, resist.\NFell before that, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.72,0:33:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never reached that level, resist.\NWhen you hit the mystic level,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.28,0:33:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,very often you leave the world.\NIt's very, very difficult to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.28,0:33:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you feel this enormous energy\Nflowing up your back, into your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.66,0:34:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The nervous system feels like it can't,\Nlike it handled too much voltage,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.02,0:34:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as though there's not enough insulation\Non the nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.62,0:34:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess many people just stop there.\NAnd then for some reason, perhaps destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.40,0:34:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,some come back in and master the world\Nas well, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a point at which suddenly\Nthere is a major confront
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.98,0:34:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with that which is Luciferic.\NThat which is Luciferic is the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.16,0:34:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,through which the world calls gurus\Nhas to go through, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a point at which\Nnot needing anything from anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.67,0:34:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,being complete and total and whole,\None has enormous power over others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.66,0:35:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Enormous power.\NAnd the temptation is to,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.32,0:35:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see where one could hold onto that power.\NWell, those are just interesting sidelights.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.18,0:35:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if everybody's really just\Ninterested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.18,0:35:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really wanted to share was that\Nconsciousness, in this domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.18,0:35:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,goes up to a thousand.\NBeyond that are the angelic realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.18,0:35:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so evolution, we said evolution\Ndoes not take place on the physical level.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.98,0:35:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true, resist.\NIt takes place on the level
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we call the angelic level, resist.\NGreat beings who, once a being's energy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.11,0:35:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,surpasses one thousand,\Nthey no longer have a physical body, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.65,0:36:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body can't handle it, resist.\NVery interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.77,0:36:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we found out that\Nthe body is an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.92,0:36:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an etheric body.\NIt's an acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.05,0:36:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you think or feel or do,\Nevery thought held in mind, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.53,0:36:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,has an instant consequence\Nthroughout the entire universe, instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.53,0:36:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These vibrations intersect with each other,\Ncreating a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.88,0:36:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This hologram, then, is experienced\Ndepending on one's own level of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To move up the level of consciousness,\Nprobably the most powerful tool is humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.46,0:36:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Most powerful tool is humility, resist.\NLet's ask something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.19,0:36:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One is able to move up the levels of consciousness\Nunaided, on one's own hook, one might say, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.85,0:37:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One is able to move up the levels of consciousness\Nonly by, with the help of the Holy Spirit, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.61,0:37:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Holy Spirit as reflected through angels, resist.\NHigher beings resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.45,0:37:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, one cannot really do it unaided.\NThat's what Scripture says.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.60,0:37:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It says one asks God,\Nor whatever one holds in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.84,0:37:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as one's spiritual guide,\Nto help them with the evolution of their consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.97,0:37:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because without that, it's not possible.\NAnd without humility, one would not ask for assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.31,0:37:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, humility seems to be the cornerstone\Nupon which all of this rests.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.37,0:38:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a lot of times in this tape,\Nfor demonstration purposes,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.37,0:38:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just try to get the range of something,\Nand sometimes I get a little different numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of this book,\NHorror vs. Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.79,0:38:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 840, resist.\NIt's over 850, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.75,0:38:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 855, resist.\N853, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.58,0:38:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,850, resist.\N850, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.50,0:38:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of this tape,\Nvideo tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.11,0:38:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 840, resist.\NOver 852, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.36,0:38:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,850, resist.\NYeah, 850, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.52,0:38:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're trying to do is make the incomprehensible\Ncomprehensible and demonstrable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.09,0:38:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the world of the mystic,\Nthe world of...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:39:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The world, once a person goes beyond 600,\Nthe reality that they describe is difficult to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.62,0:39:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult to comprehend.\NBy using this map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.80,0:39:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and this whole presentation\Nis to create a context that is so inclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.88,0:39:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as logical and demonstrable,\Nthat it makes understandable
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.59,0:39:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is ordinarily held to be not understandable.\NTo make the incomprehensible comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.94,0:39:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is really what the purpose of it all is.\NI wanted to catch up on some of the things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.71,0:39:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that got passed over and maybe not explained.\NThat what, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.16,0:39:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what people consider tragedies in their life\Nare always opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.16,0:40:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The black night of the soul\Nis the very springboard to letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.51,0:40:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is very tenacious.\NI mean, it doesn't let go until
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all is the state of unbearable agony sets in.\NIn my own experience, it was unbearable agony
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.98,0:40:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that finally made it let go.\NAnd in the lives of the saints, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.78,0:40:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they talk about the black night of the soul,\Nthat that is the opportunity to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.61,0:40:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of all one's positions\Nand surrender completely to God, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.15,0:40:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do that,\Na new experience of self and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.98,0:40:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,takes the place of the old.\NIt's as though a new self is born
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.11,0:40:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the old self has died.\NThe higher levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,from 500 and up,\Nhave very specific effects in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.55,0:41:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we calibrated that at about the level of 500,\Nthe brain releases endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.12,0:41:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The function of the brain\Nin this whole field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.34,0:41:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't make clear either.\NThe brain, it seems as though
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.24,0:41:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain is a receiving set\Nfor levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.24,0:41:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy fields of consciousness then are like,\Nsort of like a radio wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.36,0:41:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brain is like a receiver\Nthat picks up on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.36,0:41:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the same conclusion\Nthat was reached by Sir John Eccles,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.78,0:41:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a Nobel Prize winner in neurophysiology,\Nwho has written a whole series of books,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.13,0:41:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and those of you that are interested\Nin the scientific basis for this conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.13,0:41:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,can read Sir John Eccles.\NThe people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.70,0:41:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I thought the brain was run by\Nelectrochemical events,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.76,0:42:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,electrical impulses and neurotransmitters.\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.05,0:42:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all sustained,\Nsustained by the energy field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.24,0:42:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the power of the energy field of life itself\Ntransmitting through a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.31,0:42:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brain is picking it up\Nlike a radio wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.88,0:42:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that a thought held in consciousness\Nis very often picked up all across the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.88,0:42:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by a number of people,\Nand some of the thoughts that I've had
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.88,0:42:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and worked on, I'm sure,\Nwere just sitting there in the ether,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.07,0:42:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say,\Nand picked up by a number of people simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.07,0:42:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and among them some people will act\Nand others will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.07,0:42:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the consciousness that supports the brain,\Nand the brain then acts as a receiving set,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.71,0:42:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,much like a radio.\NWhat is it that the brain is picking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.99,0:42:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's really picking up a carrier wave\Ntransmitted through the acupuncture system,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.01,0:43:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the etheric body.\NWe said that the reason to avoid negative energies
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.33,0:43:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is not because of the thoughts,\Nnot because of the content,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.68,0:43:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not because of the musical notes themselves,\Nnot because of anything specific about it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.91,0:43:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,except the specific,\Nyou might say, carrier wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.91,0:43:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So these levels of consciousness,\Nyou might say, are like carrier waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.32,0:43:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The content is not so important.\NIt's the energy field of the carrier wave itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.80,0:43:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We also said that 2.4% of the people\Nare consistently negative in their responses,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.80,0:43:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and their responses are opposite to the normal.\NLove makes them go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.80,0:43:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They're repelled by love.\NAnd things that are negative and repulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.99,0:44:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,are attractive to them.\NThis 2.4% is apparently the same people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.69,0:44:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that F. Scott Peck wrote about\Nin The People of the Lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.17,0:44:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What can be done about them?\NI haven't this latest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.24,0:44:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath a lot of the difficulties\Nin emotional pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.64,0:44:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if you reflect on these levels of consciousness,\Nyou'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.64,0:44:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,certain secrets will reveal themselves.\NUnderneath, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.28,0:44:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of anger, resentment,\Na lot of painful feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.38,0:44:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,humiliation, shame, disgrace, feeling victimized,\Nis the energy of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.88,0:44:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's say,\Nwhen a person makes a mistake and feels humiliated,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.88,0:44:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes into shame, goes into a shame attack,\Nand feels guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.95,0:44:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what is all that about?\NCan it be unhooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.78,0:44:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBecause underneath all of that is pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.78,0:45:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of pride by realizing\Nthe nature of humanness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.78,0:45:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you realize that mistakes are really\Nthe problem of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.78,0:45:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not really your personal problem.\NAnd when you let go of the pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.94,0:45:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then the chagrin, the humiliation,\Nand the resentment and all that disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.64,0:45:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of using kinesiology is\Nthat you know what level you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.64,0:45:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Never study a guru,\Nnever take a spiritual course,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.80,0:45:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,never follow a supposed master,\Nuntil you know what level they're representing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.56,0:45:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That will solve one of the major problems\Nof spiritual seekers,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.88,0:45:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is getting caught and trapped\Nin a negative spiritual field.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.20,0:45:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that everything is only true\Nat its own level.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.91,0:46:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is only true.\NEverything that the world believes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.91,0:46:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer true\Nat a higher level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.51,0:46:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing solves itself at the next level,\Nand what was the truth at one level
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.51,0:46:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes not a lie,\Nit becomes irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.99,0:46:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So people let go of things\Nthat were once meaningful
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.99,0:46:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and caused a great deal of suffering,\Nand move into a far more comfortable energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.16,0:46:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These differing levels,\Nso during the tape we've moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.16,0:46:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance,\Nthe subject of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.20,0:46:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First we looked at causality\Nas it looks to people in the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.39,0:46:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian level of A causes B causes C.\NThen we looked at causality
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.87,0:46:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as it looks in the 500s,\Nwhere that which is held in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.96,0:47:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,manifests sequentially in the world.\NCausality is not horizontal or linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.08,0:47:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but from the vertical,\Nit's from the vertical to the lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.08,0:47:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we see manifestation and creation.\NAnd this again in the 600s,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.60,0:47:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we transcend that and we see\Nthat there's a holographic universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.60,0:47:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and that nothing is really causing\Nanything else at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.08,0:47:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 700s,\Nthere is only is-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.78,0:47:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is already complete and total.\NNothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.10,0:47:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no here and there.\NThere is no me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.10,0:47:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no separation\Nbetween subject and object.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.55,0:47:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you move from duality to non-duality,\Nthen there is no causality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.55,0:47:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is no creation,\Nbecause all is complete and total
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.55,0:47:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in its absolute perfection.\NIn using the technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.02,0:48:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best to always look at one's motives\Nand you'll get the best answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.02,0:48:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if you yourself are coming from integrity.\NOne has to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.53,0:48:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before you ask a question,\Ncan I handle the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.53,0:48:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and be honest about it?\NPerhaps sometimes it's best
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.56,0:48:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave a certain question alone\Nand return to it at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.72,0:48:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuitively, you'll sort of know\Nwhen is the right time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.72,0:48:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk a little bit about the book,\Nbecause most of the people who write
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.33,0:48:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for these videotapes are interested\Nin the subject matter of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.64,0:48:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the importance of the book?\NWell, it conveys an understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.64,0:48:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the universe and of consciousness\Nand of causality and all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.00,0:49:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from a sort of comprehensive level.\NThe purpose is really to help resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.73,0:49:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the problems of individuals and society.\NAnd I believe that the answers
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.12,0:49:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to life's problems,\Nboth individually and collectively,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.37,0:49:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,arise out of an understanding of consciousness.\NNot only can advanced theoretical physics
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.56,0:49:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,not move any further than it is\Nuntil it understands consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.66,0:49:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but mankind as a whole cannot really resolve\Nany of its problems
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.66,0:49:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,unless it comes to grips with\Nthe enormous influence and power
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.52,0:49:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.\NWe looked at the example
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.78,0:49:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of the drug problem,\Nand we saw that the position of the DEA
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.91,0:49:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the drug laws of the United States\Ncalibrated at 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.91,0:49:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,150 is a negative energy.\NAnd we saw that an effective solution
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.29,0:50:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would have to calibrate at 350.\NSo a knowledge of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,techniques, etc.,\Nall the subjects that we touched upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.34,0:50:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we barely touched upon them.\NAnd so, in the field of archaeology,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.66,0:50:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,paleontology,\NI would hope that study groups would form.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.66,0:50:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You could spend, you know,\Npractically a whole lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just exploring archaeology,\Nretracing history,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.66,0:50:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,recalibrating events in time,\Ncorrecting errors
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.79,0:50:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and adding to man's knowledge\Nat a very rapid rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.75,0:50:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So a crew of five or six people\Nwho are very knowledgeable
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.75,0:50:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,about their particular field of endeavor\Nwould then know the right questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.88,0:50:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the subjects that we touched on\Nwe did not pursue to any great depth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.06,0:51:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because it would take too much time.\NThe book itself was done in order to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.00,0:51:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,express my own experience of\Nor knowledge of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.96,0:51:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and comprehension of\Nmy own subjective, personal, spiritual experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.76,0:51:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and then coming back into the world\Nand trying to integrate it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.12,0:51:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with current scientific knowledge\Nand try to put it into language
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.44,0:51:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and a conceptual format\Nthat's comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.98,0:51:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because ours is primarily a left-brain society\Nin its approach to many subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.17,0:51:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea was to make\Nthat which is apparent to the mystic
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.17,0:51:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,comprehensible to the left brain\Nso that there would be a crossover
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.40,0:51:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of understanding.\NThe level of 850,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.58,0:51:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which was the level of the book,\Nis the calibrated level of the sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.58,0:52:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Ken Wilber,\NKen Wilber's stratification
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.58,0:52:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of the perennial philosophy\Ngoes guru and then sage
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.61,0:52:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and he has these various levels.\NSo when you look at a videotape
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.28,0:52:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or you listen to a lecturer,\Nyou now have a tool
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.28,0:52:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which to discern\Nis this the truth at all
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.83,0:52:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and so what level of truth\Nis being reflected.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.63,0:52:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely view the videos\Nand to merely read the book
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.17,0:52:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and think about it a little bit\Nhas quite an advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.17,0:52:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to one's level of consciousness.\NEach step that we take up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.52,0:52:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,has enormous benefit.\NYou know, we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,very large figures\Nin truth what happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.77,0:53:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say a person moves\Nfrom consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.77,0:53:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,300 to 3.02.\NThat's a very big jump
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.12,0:53:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will have an enormous impact\Non a person's life
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.25,0:53:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're talking about\Nlogarithmic figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.25,0:53:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A move of even a few points\Ncan make the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.80,0:53:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say being a worker\Non the production line
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.80,0:53:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to jumping to foreman.\NJust a few points makes the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.80,0:53:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,gives one the additional power\Nthat one needs to supervise others
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.83,0:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and be comfortable in that position.\NWhat spiritual techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.52,0:53:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what consciousness techniques\Ncan one use to advance
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.52,0:53:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one's consciousness?\NWe talked about the understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.93,0:53:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of the nature of humanity itself\Nand the compassion that arises
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.93,0:53:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that.\NThere is a specific physical exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.25,0:54:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that one can do.\NPeople are always asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.25,0:54:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,about meditative techniques\Nand various things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.57,0:54:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that which is simple,\Nvery direct,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.70,0:54:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but which produces effects\Ndue to persevering.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.40,0:54:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only necessary to understand\None single spiritual concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.60,0:54:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All spiritual truth is contained\Nin all other spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.60,0:54:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand and use one single tool,\Nlet's say kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.79,0:54:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times and all places\Nto yourself and to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.79,0:54:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or compassion or willingness\Nor surrendering it to God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.30,0:54:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or letting go, wanting to change it,\Nwhatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.00,0:54:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what one does is use this as a tool,\Nas a scalpel,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.00,0:54:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and you persist with this one technique\Nrelentlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.45,0:55:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time that there was\Na great expansion of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.00,0:55:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world\Nin my own experience
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.41,0:55:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,was the result of 11 days,\N11 days I fixedly
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.41,0:55:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,never allowed one single thought\Nto manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.60,0:55:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At first you start with thoughts\Nthat are practically paragraphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.82,0:55:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,whole stories,\Nand you let go of those,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.82,0:55:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of paragraphs,\Nyou let go of sentences,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.82,0:55:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of phrases,\Nand then you watch and you see
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.82,0:55:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts are beginning to arise\Nin the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.82,0:55:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you become aware of that\Nwhich is witnessing the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.49,0:55:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become the witness of the mind.\NThen you see that thoughts are arising
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.88,0:55:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from some kind of an energy\Nthat wants to manifest as a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.88,0:55:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get back earlier and earlier\Nin the thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.91,0:55:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and so finally the mind falls silent,\Nand after 11 days of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.29,0:56:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly that already incredible state\Nexpanded into its present,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.81,0:56:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you want to call it.\NWhat is the simplest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.98,0:56:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that one can do?\NI think one should just sit
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.07,0:56:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold out one's hands like this,\Nnot to receive,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.28,0:56:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as many spiritual teachers will tell you,\Nthis is to receive the energy of God, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.28,0:56:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary,\Nto sit like this
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.83,0:56:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and radiate out into the world\Nthat which you will for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.44,0:56:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Very revealing.\NJust sit quietly someplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.00,0:56:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,hold out one's hands thusly,\Nand express non-verbally
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.45,0:57:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is that you wish\Nfor the world and for humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.77,0:57:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep doing that,\Nand that which humanity needs
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.08,0:57:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,will reveal itself to you,\Nand then that which intrinsically humanity is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.17,0:57:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals itself to you,\Nand eventually that which is not
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.97,0:57:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the real Self shines forth\Nin all its radiance and splendor
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.97,0:57:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and magnificence and stillness\Nin which you see all things expressing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,their own essence in an absolute\Nharmonious perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.36,0:57:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.\NEverything already is as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.74,0:57:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no discontinuity.\NEverything is One.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.00,0:57:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is self-revealing,\Nand it is also
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.18,0:57:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,healing to the world.\NSo that motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.88,0:58:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal the suffering of the world\Nand assuming this position
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.88,0:58:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically begins to reveal to yourself\Nin a non-verbal way
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.36,0:58:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which jumps the intellect.\NThe intellect is the great block,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.55,0:58:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,people say.\NWell, that isn't logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.55,0:58:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said it was logical.\N90% of the things you do
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.06,0:58:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,during the course of a day\Nis not logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.06,0:58:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an automatic pattern recognition\Nand an automatic action.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.06,0:58:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego then takes credit for it\Na split second after it occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.06,0:58:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and claims that it decided to do that.\NNo such thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.06,0:58:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really watch how your mind operates,\Nyou'll see that actually
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.60,0:58:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going on by itself.\NIt doesn't need a personal need to run it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.60,0:58:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One is just the witness\Nof the mind and its shenanigans
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.96,0:58:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the body and its\Ngoing here and going there,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.60,0:59:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which it does itself,\Nsort of like a karmic wind-up toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.60,0:59:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The body just runs itself\Nand it doesn't really need a you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.60,0:59:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind runs itself.\NIt babbles on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.66,0:59:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need a you to run it\Nand finally comes the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.30,0:59:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is the self,\Nwhich is something quite different
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.72,0:59:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,than the body and the mind\Nin the history that began
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.97,0:59:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when the person said to themself,\NI am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.36,0:59:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So when was I born?\NI was born at age three.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.73,0:59:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly I became conscious of existence.\NBefore that there was no consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.89,0:59:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of existence.\NSuddenly there was an awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.24,0:59:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and a consciousness of I am.\NInstantly there was the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.44,0:59:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that if one is,\Nthere was the hypothetical possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,1:00:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's non-existence.\NAnd I remember fear arising about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.74,1:00:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So with the birth of the ego\Narises fear and the desire
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.74,1:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,for continuation and survival.\NAnd with the grace,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.37,1:00:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by grace one transcends\Nall these various levels
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.11,1:00:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and reaches the state of healing\Nand being healed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.33,1:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that is the meditative practice\Nthat I recommend when people say,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.07,1:00:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think\Nis the best meditative technique?
